sentences.sentence: P&G applied for a patent on its cookies.
sentences.translation: 宝洁公司为其饼干申请了专利。

sentences.sentence: You get to sample lots of baked things and take home masses of cookies besides.
sentences.translation: 你可以品尝许多烘烤食品，此外还能带许多饼干回家。

sentences.sentence: There are only five cookies left.
